Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1

Thanks Cyril,

Really like the direction of this. It seems that we're running all of our tests with set number of workers. Would you mind to write a test that would test we actually do get the correct number of workers spunn up when the config is populated with 'None'?

Probably best references how to approach this would be found from the reload functional tests https://github.com/openstack/glance/blob/master/glance/tests/functional/test_reload.py#L118 onwards and our test server config: https://github.com/openstack/glance/blob/master/glance/tests/functional/__init__.py#L278-L369
